  Decision at 5% level:
    Fov: Reject H0 => Evidence of a long-run relationship
    t:   Reject H0 => Dependent variable participates in ECM
         (rules out degenerate case #1)
    Find: Reject H0 => Independent variables enter long-run
          (rules out degenerate case #2)
